{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE</h2>Explore a living, colorful world, ranging from dense forests to dark caves.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/Explore_short.gif?t=1636537260\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUILD</h2>Your cabin grows with you: build new rooms to unlock additional game mechanics, including cooking, gardening, crafting and sewing.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/build_short.gif?t=1636537260\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GROW</h2>Nurture delicate (and delicious) plants in your greenhouse. Eat them raw or make a stew for better nutritional values.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/rename_planting_short.gif?t=1636537260\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVE</h2>Dangerous animals roam some areas in the woods. Better keep a distance if you can. <br><i>(Among Trees also includes a ZEN mode without dangerous animals)</i><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/survive_short_bear.gif?t=1636537260\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BEST FRIENDS FOREVER</h2>While the wilderness can be dangerous, it doesn't mean you can\u2019t make new friends. Adopt a Fox Pet who you can feed, pet, and train to help you find loot.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/fox_pet.gif?t=1636537260\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the Wild","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/897730/f3001d24a636884ef9ecb11cb0fff2b00ede81f6.jpg"},{"name":"Two Weeks in the Woods","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/897730/d4b0339726227f72a2aaf89aeb645c74b311d62b.jpg"},{"name":"Walden","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam